### Suppliers tests

### Get all suppliers
GET {{host}}/Suppliers/getSuppliers

### Get supplier by ID (existing: 1)
GET {{host}}/Suppliers/getSupplierByID/1

### Get supplier by name (existing example: "Acme Foods")
GET {{host}}/Suppliers/getSupplierByName/Acme%20Foods

### Get supplier for Wiener Schnitzel
